text: Oliver Spasovski (; born 21 October 1976) is a Macedonian politician. He was the Prime Minister of North Macedonia. Until 3 January 2020, Spasovski was Minister of Internal Affairs.North Macedonian PM resigns By NEKTARIA STAMOULI, Politico, January 3, 2020 He is general secretary of the Social Democratic Union of Macedonia (SDSM). ==References== Category:1976 births Category:Living people Category:Prime Ministers of North Macedonia
